{{IPA notice}}

This article describes the '''[[phonology]]''' of the '''[[Somali language]]'''.

==Consonants==
Common Somali has 23 consonant [[phoneme]]s. Its consonants cover every place of articulation on the [[International Phonetic Alphabet|IPA]] chart, though not all of these distinctions are phonemic.

