* Elias, Justine. (September 15, 2009). [http://thephoenix.com/boston/arts/89683-plain-talk/ Plain talk: Jesse Sheidlower gives the f-word its due.] ''The Boston Phoenix''. * Sheidlower, Jesse. (2009). [https://books.google.com/books?id=I_AGK-49nlcC ''The F-word''] (third edition). New York: Oxford University Press US.
